data.description:
Discover this charming 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom townhome available for rent in the sought-after Victory Lakes/Pembrooke community. It's a fantastic opportunity to enjoy a comfortable lifestyle with great amenities. The main floor and basement feature recessed lighting, creating a warm ambiance. The main floor also boasts beautiful hardwood floors, and a spacious 12X19 Trex deck for relaxing evenings and seamless outdoor entertaining with friends and family.

The fully equipped gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances and a large granite island is perfect for homework or family dinners. Upstairs, the primary bedroom is a tranquil retreat with tray ceilings, an ensuite bathroom featuring a double sink vanity, and a walk-in shower. Each bedroom is equipped with fans and lights, and there's the added convenience of bedroom-level laundry.

Moving to the lower level, you'll find a full bathroom, vinyl plank flooring, and access to a delightful patio in the fully fenced backyard. 

The landlord covers the HOA fees, providing access to a fitness center, clubhouse, pools, a tot lot, basketball and tennis courts, and picnic areas. Conveniently located near grocery stores, cafes, restaurants, I-66, 28, and 29, this townhome ensures easy living. Commuting is a breeze with the Virginia Rail Express (VRE). Don't miss this opportunity to live in a stylish, comfortable, and convenient home!

1 or 2-year lease duration.
Smoke-free home
